  LINKS

To add a link in ur app u need libary "net/url", command url.Parse() and, to add it in our app, widget.NewHyperLink()

For example: 
url, _ := url.Parse("https://web.telegram.org/k/#@biberanddol1k")

link := widget.NewHyperlink("Telegram", url)

The second var is error. We can skip it or process it.

 
  IMAGES

To add a image on your web app u need to use canvas libary and command window.SetContent(container.NewGridWithColumns())
First var will be numbers of columns/rows, following will be ur images or sth

For exapmle:
image1 := canvas.NewImageFromFile("Screenshot_3.png")
label := widget.NewLabel("Image")
window.SetContent(container.NewGridWithColumns(2, image1, label))
